\v 10 <a name="01800701000002" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000:Negators">لاَ</a> <a name="01800701000004" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023:Move">يَرْجعُ</a> <a name="01800701000006">بَعْدُ</a> إِلَى <a name="01800701000010" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000003:Groups">بَيْتِهِ</a>، <a name="01800701000014" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000:Negators">وَلاَ</a> <a name="01800701000016" ll="SDBH:נכר:000000:Know">يَعْرِفُهُ</a> <a name="01800701000020" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000:Space">مَكَانُهُ</a> <a name="01800701000018">بَعْدُ</a>.
