\v 29 <a name="01803002900004">صِرْتُ</a> <a name="01803002900002" ll="SDBH:אָח:000003:Friends">أَخًا</a> لِلذِّئَابِ، وَصَاحِبًا <a name="01803002900016" ll="SDBH:בַּת:002000:" il="Fauna:3.16">لِرِئَالِ</a> <a name="01803002900018" ll="SDBH:יַעֲנָה:000000:Birds" il="Bengalese_Eagle_Owl;Bolen00333;Fauna0034;Fauna0035">ٱلنَّعَامِ</a>.
