\v 22 مِنَ <a name="01803702200004" ll="SDBH:צָפֹון:000001:Orientation">ٱلشَّمَالِ</a> <a name="01803702200008" ll="SDBH:אתה:000002:Happen">يَأْتِي</a> <a name="01803702200006" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000001:Shine">ذَهَبٌ</a>. عِنْدَ <a name="01803702200012" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹוהַּ:000001:Deities" tl="HOTTP2041">ٱللّٰهِ</a> <a name="01803702200016" ll="SDBH:הֹוד:000000:Great" tl="HOTTP2041">جَلاَلٌ</a> <a name="01803702200014" ll="SDBH:ירא:000001:Afraid" tl="HOTTP2041">مُرْهِبٌ</a>.
